get.description:
        Retrieve all elements of a model with a simple value representation
        Format response :
            {
                :element_uuid: {
                    "attributes": {
                        :property_name: value,
                        :property_name: value
                    },
                    :property_set_name: {
                        :property_name: value,
                        :property_name: value
                    }
                }
            }

Required scopes: ifc:read

